				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Ban-Si%C3%AAu-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-b%C3%BAt/poem-UtnwF_In8O8EoZGDsQ0Xwg">Ban Siêu đầu bút - 班超投筆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/Giang-Nam-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-DvRsGNj21qU2Dth-HqmtvQ">Giang Nam khúc kỳ 5 - 江南曲其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/author-oVwYIEYCT983JTs6qs8v3A">Lưu Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Ho%E1%BA%A1-L%C3%BD-m%E1%BA%ADu-t%C3%A0i-thi/poem-DWpbY9HA_tWyxf7XWv3mDQ">Hoạ Lý mậu tài thi - 和李茂才詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BB%81u-Tri-Chi/L%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2u-thi%C3%AAn/poem-NczRs8cD5CRQb8MuBmY5wg">Lục Châu thiên - 綠珠篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BB%81u-Tri-Chi/author-Lsg5FCAGLlUg9HfTUhcnjw">Kiều Tri Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/Mai/poem-6gmhx1js8emwkShgA3awWw">Mai - 梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/author-lVq0c6nfaKZdZ1zJHdkYzA">Diệp Nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-xbJhFsFuXmvOJnXyf9d5fg">Tái hạ khúc kỳ 1 - 塞下曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/author-Q_JpPOHTIyzNkB76eQk-WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BA%A7m-t%C6%B0-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-u87I_yOcxJGwrqgYnu0NXQ">Tầm tư thiếu niên nhật - 尋思少年日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-_7CqmIso_KPrgdZzKRq2pw">Tịch thượng hữu tặng - 席上有贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-ca/poem-FZsX7_qZDzP98yT1BN2IFA">Vương Chiêu Quân ca - 王昭君歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
